step 1: create the module folder

step 2: create the etc/module.xml file

step 3: create the registration.php file

step 4: 
bin/magento module:enable module_name
bin/magento setup:upgrade
(script to install the new module)

step 5: check that the module is working
(config.php 'name-module'=>1)

bin/magento cache:clean



